Morning routine habits for a productive day:
♡ Put on a cute workout outfit to feel motivated
♡ Wash your face with freezing cold water to wake up
♡ Get Sunshine ASAP 🌞 
♡ Turn on DND the night before (I don’t look at any screens during the first 1-2 hrs of the morning)
♡ Walk or any kind of movement first thing for creative brainstorming, energy, improved mental clarity & focus 
♡ Read or journal affirmations
♡ Plan your day: write out your priority tasks — Get my PRINTABLE PLANNER that I designed to help you maintain focus, enhance productivity & achieve your goals BossGirlsSociety.com (link in bio) 

♥︎ I wrote a full blog post with more tips & all the deets on the top most effective tips that I personally do every morning (I feel amazing every single time I do this morning routine!) — Read the blog post over on BossGirlsSociety.com
